---

## ğŸ”Œ API Endpoints

### Base URL
```
http://localhost:5000/api/movies
```

### Endpoints

| Method | Endpoint | Description | Request Body |
|--------|----------|-------------|--------------|
| `GET` | `/` | Get all movies | - |
| `GET` | `/:id` | Get single movie by ID | - |
| `POST` | `/` | Create new movie | `multipart/form-data` |
| `PUT` | `/:id` | Update existing movie | `multipart/form-data` |
| `DELETE` | `/:id` | Delete movie | - |
| `GET` | `/search?q=query` | Search movies by title | - |

