---


## ğŸ“„ Pages

### 1. Movie List (Index)
**Route**: `/`

| Feature | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| Grid Layout | Responsive movie card grid |
| Search | Filter movies by title |
| Add Movie | Button to open add form |
| View/Edit/Delete | Actions on each card |

### 2. Not Found
**Route**: `/*`

- 404 error page for invalid routes

---

## ğŸ§© Components

### MovieCard
Displays individual movie information in a card format.

```jsx
<MovieCard 
  movie={movieData}
  onView={() => handleView(id)}
  onEdit={() => handleEdit(id)}
  onDelete={() => handleDelete(id)}
/>
```

**Props:**
| Prop | Type | Description |
|------|------|-------------|
| movie | Object | Movie data object |
| onView | Function | View button callback |
| onEdit | Function | Edit button callback |
| onDelete | Function | Delete button callback |

---

### MovieForm
Form for adding or editing movies.

```jsx
<MovieForm
  movie={existingMovie}  // null for new movie
  onSubmit={handleSubmit}
  onCancel={handleCancel}
  isLoading={isSubmitting}
/>
```

**Props:**
| Prop | Type | Description |
|------|------|-------------|
| movie | Object/null | Existing movie data or null |
| onSubmit | Function | Form submission handler |
| onCancel | Function | Cancel button callback |
| isLoading | Boolean | Loading state for submit |

---

### MovieDetails
Displays full movie details in a modal/panel.

```jsx
<MovieDetails
  movie={selectedMovie}
  onClose={handleClose}
  onEdit={handleEdit}
  onDelete={handleDelete}
/>
```

---

### SearchInput
Search input with debounced filtering.

```jsx
<SearchInput
  value={searchQuery}
  onChange={setSearchQuery}
  placeholder="Search movies..."
/>
```

---

## ğŸª Hooks

### useMovies
Custom hook for movie CRUD operations.

```jsx
const {
  movies,           // Array of movies
  isLoading,        // Loading state
  error,            // Error state
  addMovie,         // Function to add movie
  updateMovie,      // Function to update movie
  deleteMovie,      // Function to delete movie
  searchMovies      // Function to search movies
} = useMovies();
```

---

## ğŸ”Œ API Service

### movieService.js

```javascript
// API Base URL (update for production)
const API_BASE_URL = 'http://localhost:5000/api/movies';

// Available Methods
movieService.getAll()              // GET all movies
movieService.getById(id)           // GET single movie
movieService.create(formData)      // POST new movie
movieService.update(id, formData)  // PUT update movie
movieService.delete(id)            // DELETE movie
movieService.search(query)         // GET search results
```

